American Ninja (Joe Armstrong), a highly skilled martial arts warrior, takes on mercenaries in the Philippines with the assistance of his Army colleague, Curtis Jackson.

*American Ninja 2 - The Confrontation* &lt;a href=&quot;
http://us.imdb.com/title/tt0092548/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://us.imdb.com/title/tt0092548/&lt;/a&gt;
On a remote Caribbean island, Joe Armstrong returns to save an old friend from the clutches of &quot;The Lion&quot;, an evil super-criminal who has kidnapped a local scientist and mass-produced an army of genetically engineered Ninja warriors.

*American Ninja 3 - Blood Hunt* &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0096804/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0096804/&lt;/a&gt;
Curtis Jackson is back, and is joined by his new partner and American Ninja, Sean Davidson. They must face a deadly terrorist known as &quot;The Cobra&quot; and his army of Ninja's intent on committing a vile act of genocide.

*American Ninja 4 - The Annihilation* &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0101326/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0101326/&lt;/a&gt;
Joe Armstrong and Sean Davidson (The American Ninja's) team up to take on a twisted duo of Mulgrew and Maksood and their army of Ninja's. Their mission is to prevent these sick terrorists from detonating a nuclear bomb in New York.

*American Ninja 5* &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0106257/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0106257/&lt;/a&gt;
Joe teams up with child ninja, Hiro. Together they set out to rescue a kidnapped scientist and his daughter from the evil businessman 'Glock', who wants to sell nerve gas to a terrorist. They are confronted by his private army of ninja assassins, led by the fierce ninja master known as 'Viper'.
